>I tried to find some information on who invented the word
>"mutex" and when it was first used, but failed miserably. Any
>information or advice on where to look for such information
>will be appreciated.

Dijkstra used it as a mutual exclusion semaphore variable name in
his 1965 paper Cooperating Sequential Processes
http://www.cs.utexas.edu/users/EWD/ewd01xx/EWD123.PDF

